Privacy Policy for Flipo Application

At Flipo, we value the privacy and security of our users' personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect the information you provide while using our shopping app for used items. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your personal data.

Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information: When you use our shopping app, we may collect personal information such as your name, email address, contact number, and shipping address. This information is necessary for the completion of purchases and the delivery of items.

1.2 Usage Data: We may collect certain information automatically when you interact with our app, including your IP address, device information, browsing activity, and app usage statistics. This data helps us analyze user behavior, improve our services, and provide a better user experience.

How We Use Your Information
2.1 Transaction Processing: We use your personal information to process your purchases, facilitate payments, and deliver the items to your specified address.

2.2 Communication: We may use your contact information to communicate with you regarding your orders, provide customer support, and send important updates or notifications related to our services.

2.3 Personalization: We may analyze your usage data to personalize your experience on our app, recommend relevant products, and display targeted advertisements that align with your interests.

2.4 Legal Compliance: In certain cases, we may be required to use and disclose your personal information to comply with legal obligations, respond to lawful requests, or protect our rights and interests.

Data Security
We take appropriate measures to safeguard your personal information and protect it against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. We use industry-standard security protocols, encryption, and secure server infrastructure to ensure the confidentiality and integrity of your data.

Third-Party Services
Our shopping app may integrate with third-party services, such as payment gateways or delivery partners, to facilitate transactions and fulfill orders. Please note that these third-party services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review their terms and practices.

Data Retention
We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, comply with legal obligations, and resolve disputes. Once the information is no longer required, we securely delete or anonymize it.

Your Rights
You have the right to access, update, correct, or delete the personal information we hold about you. If you have any concerns or wish to exercise your rights, please contact us using the information provided at the end of this policy.

Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any significant updates by email or through app notifications. Please review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we handle your information.

Contact Us
If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:

